               <msContents>
                  <summary>Acts of Täklä Haymanot, ገድለ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ; Twelve Miracles of Täklä Haymanot, ተአምረ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</summary>
